Name Rascal/Libraries/Vis/Figure/Figures/computeFigure

Function computeFigure(Figure () computeFig, FProperty props...)
Description The figure that is returned by the callback computeFig. Subsequent calls to computeFig may return different figures and may thus change the resulting visualization. The figure is recomputed after each user interaction.
